      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with plenty of life left? This car is a solid find that\u2019s ready to get you where you need to go! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a functional and practical choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s a well-loved vehicle that\u2019s perfect for someone who appreciates a car with character and a proven track record!",
