      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This S54-powered icon features a factory-spec 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, showing zero Vanos rattle and recently serviced rod bearings. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and pristine bushings that maintain original suspension geometry and lateral stiffness. The Getrag 6-speed manual provides precise engagement, paired with a perfectly functioning variable M-differential. Every mechanical system, from the cooling stack to the DSC sensors, operates at peak performance. This is a turn-key, mechanically transparent example for the discerning enthusiast.",
